</taxonomicName>
. 
<emphasis id="3592EA9F0B7A164B7A51F8422541F83C" bold="true" box="[516,539,1920,1941]" pageId="10" pageNumber="115">A.</emphasis>
Flower. 
<emphasis id="3592EA9F0B7A164B7A3AF84225DFF83C" bold="true" box="[623,645,1920,1941]" pageId="10" pageNumber="115">B.</emphasis>
Abaxial surface of leaf. 
