Adaxial surface of leaf. 
<emphasis id="3592EA9F0B7A164B7C24F84223D3F83C" bold="true" box="[1137,1161,1920,1941]" pageId="10" pageNumber="115">D.</emphasis>
Mature schizocarp. 
