<emphasis id="3592EA9F0B7A164B79C1F80A26F9F874" bold="true" box="[404,419,1992,2013]" pageId="10" pageNumber="115">I.</emphasis>
Schizocarps and buds in terminal umbelliform inflorescence 
<emphasis id="3592EA9F0B7A164B7BACF80A2351F874" bold="true" box="[1017,1035,1992,2013]" pageId="10" pageNumber="115">J.</emphasis>
